Hi all,

One more bug in Pixmap on GWT from me :)

When we set `Pixmap.setBlending(Pixmap.Blending.None)`, only last shape which we draw on texture will be showed. 

We can reproduce this bug by adding 

```
pixmap = new Pixmap(800, 480, Pixmap.Format.RGBA8888); // Pixmap.Format.RGBA8888);
Pixmap.setBlending(Pixmap.Blending.None);
// Create a texture to contain the pixmap
texture = new Texture(1024, 1024, Pixmap.Format.RGBA8888); // Pixmap.Format.RGBA8888);
```

